text: A wonderful church! Pastor Peter and Sister Cheryl are a sincere, God-fearing couple. The church is rooted in the Word of God, and they are very hospitable!

Jeshurun Assembly is a family church where everyone is friendly and cares for one another. You can experience the love in Jeshurun Assembly, and the Pastor and leaders will take care of you if you need any spiritual guidance.

Great place with a down to earth pastor.
A place I would recommend for those who is looking for a place to grow & stay real.
Keep up the good work, Ps. Peter & Sister Cheryl.
